<section class="mx-auto mb-10 max-w-[840px] text-center">
  <h1 class="mb-4 text-[48px] tracking-[-0.03em]">See AI readiness without the noise.</h1>
  <p class="text-[18px] leading-[1.7] text-[var(--muted-foreground)]">
    AICO gives deal teams a clear, consistent view of AI maturity across every company.
    One simple assessment, one shared story, fewer loose ends.
  </p>
  <div class="mt-6">
    <%= link_to "Get started", signin_path, class: "inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)] px-5 py-2.5 font-semibold text-[var(--primary-foreground)] shadow-[0_12px_24px_rgba(31,111,91,0.18)]" %>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mb-12 grid grid-cols-2 gap-10 text-[16px] text-[#1f2933] max-[900px]:grid-cols-1">
  <div>
    <p class="mt-0">
      There are plenty of AI checklists and maturity models. Most are sprawling,
      inconsistent, or buried in spreadsheets.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-0 font-semibold">
      AICO keeps the assessment tight, the scoring consistent, and the results easy to share.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <p class="mt-0">
      Assess once, compare across the portfolio, and revisit with confidence.
      Your operators see where to focus, and your partners get a clean summary.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-0">
      No decks full of caveats. No arguing over definitions. Just signal.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-[900px]:grid-cols-1">
  <div class="rounded-[18px] border border-[var(--border)] bg-[#fffaf3] p-[30px] shadow-[0_18px_40px_rgba(31,41,51,0.08)]">
    <h2 class="text-[20px]">How it works</h2>
    <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3">
      <li>Create an assessment in minutes.</li>
      <li>Send a single link to the assessor.</li>
      <li>Review the AICO score and drill into modules.</li>
      <li>Compare across companies with a consistent lens.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="rounded-[18px] border border-[var(--border)] bg-[#fffaf3] p-[30px] shadow-[0_18px_40px_rgba(31,41,51,0.08)]">
    <h2 class="text-[20px]">What you get</h2>
    <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3">
      <li>A clear signal on AI posture, not just anecdotes.</li>
      <li>Progress you can track across teams and time.</li>
      <li>Outputs that travel easily in memos and IC decks.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
